token_lists.title: NEO's Consignment Crew
token_lists.description:
A coin reveals its choice once resting upon one side.

Has this crew has come to save you, or to hasten your demise?

Wreckage? Behind them. Future? Ahead of them. What decides which direction they will choose? 
That new shipment of anti-dragon armor they found on an abandoned cargo vessel, will they cover their tracks and sell it for a little hot money? or return it for consignment in Neo's warehouse? ...sometimes the answer to a tricky question is best determined by the flipping of a coin.
